name: datagather.R
content:
#Data
VME_pts    <- read.csv("VME_pts.csv",header=TRUE)
Seamount2024<-read.csv("data2024.csv",header=TRUE)

#Models
tong_gorgonian<-rast("tong_gorgonian.tif")
yesson_gorgonian<-rast("yesson_gorgonian.tif")
chu_gorgonian<-rast("chu_gorgonian.tif")
rooper_gorgonian<-rast("rooper_gorgonian.tif")
csquare_gorgonian<-rast("csquare_gorgonian.tif")
yesson_antipatharian<-rast("yesson_antipatharia.tif")
chu_antipatharian<-rast("chu_antipatharia.tif")
rooper_antipatharian<-rast("rooper_antipatharian.tif")
csquare_antipatharian<-rast("csquare_antipatharian.tif")
gorgonian_stack<-c(csquare_gorgonian/max(values(csquare_gorgonian),na.rm=TRUE),yesson_gorgonian/max(values(yesson_gorgonian),na.rm=TRUE),tong_gorgonian/max(values(tong_gorgonian),na.rm=TRUE),chu_gorgonian/max(values(chu_gorgonian),na.rm=TRUE),rooper_gorgonian/max(values(rooper_gorgonian),na.rm=TRUE))
names(gorgonian_stack)<-c("C-squares (observations)","Yesson et al. 2012","Tong et al. 2023","Chu et al. 2019","Rooper et al. 2024")
antipatharian_stack<-c(csquare_antipatharian/max(values(csquare_antipatharian),na.rm=TRUE),yesson_antipatharian/max(values(yesson_antipatharian),na.rm=TRUE),chu_antipatharian/max(values(chu_antipatharian),na.rm=TRUE),rooper_antipatharian/max(values(rooper_antipatharian),na.rm=TRUE))
names(antipatharian_stack)<-c("C-squares (observations)","Yesson et al. 2017","Chu et al. 2019","Rooper et al. 2024")

#Base_map
cobb_basemap<-raster("cobb_basemap")
conlevels<-seq(500,5000,500)
cobbcontour<-rasterToContour(cobb_basemap,levels=conlevels)
cobbcontour<-st_as_sf(cobbcontour)

taxa<-c("Gorgonians","Antipatharians")

name: plot_functions.R
content:
library(terra)
library(raster)
library(sf)
library(cartography)
library(tidyr)
library(PresenceAbsence)
library(ggplot2)
library(tidyterra)
library(ggspatial)
library(gridExtra)
library(viridis)


 
make_map<-function(myrasters){

  
  #myrasters<-antipatharia_stack
  
  myplots<-list()  
  
  for(i in 1:dim(myrasters)[3]){
    if(dim(myrasters)[3]>1){myraster<-myrasters[[i]]}  
    if(dim(myrasters)[3]==1){myraster<-myrasters}
    
    p<-ggplot()+
      #basemap
      # geom_sf(data = bg)+
      geom_spatraster(data=myraster)+
      geom_sf(data=cobbcontour,color="grey40")+
      # annotate("text",x=-Inf,y=Inf,hjust=-0.25,vjust=1,label=seamounts_to_plot[i])+
      coord_sf(xlim = c(extent(cobb_basemap)[1],extent(cobb_basemap)[2]), 
               ylim = c(extent(cobb_basemap)[3],extent(cobb_basemap)[4]), 
               expand = TRUE)+
      
      xlab("")+ylab("")+
      
      annotation_north_arrow(location = "br", width = unit(.5, "cm"),
                             height = unit(1., "cm"),
                             style = north_arrow_orienteering(
                               line_width = 1,
                               line_col = "black",
                               fill = c("white", "black"),
                               text_col = "black",
                               text_family = "",
                               text_face = NULL,
                               text_size = 10,
                               text_angle = 0)) +
      
      scale_fill_viridis(option="plasma",name="Std. Prob.")+
      ggtitle(names(myraster))+
      #  scale_fill_viridis_d(option = "plasma",guide="none")+labs(color="VME group",fill="Depth (m)")+
      #       fill = 'Presence', 
      #      color = 'Presence')+
      theme_dark()+theme(panel.grid = element_blank(),legend.position = c(0.9,0.2),plot.margin = unit(c(.05,.05,.25,.25),"pt"),axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 0, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1,size=5),axis.text.y=element_text(size=5))#+
    #  if(i==1){theme(panel.grid = element_blank(),legend.position=c(.75,.5),legend.justification = "left")}
    
    #
    myplots[[i]]<-ggplotGrob(p)
  }
  return(myplots)
}

make_vme_plot<-function(myrasters){
  
  #myrasters<-antipatharia_stack
  
  myplots<-list()  
  
  for(i in 1:dim(myrasters)[3]){
    if(dim(myrasters)[3]>1){myraster<-myrasters[[i]]}  
    if(dim(myrasters)[3]==1){myraster<-myrasters}
    
    p<-ggplot()+
      #basemap
      # geom_sf(data = bg)+
      geom_spatraster(data=myraster)+
      geom_sf(data=cobbcontour,color="grey40")+
      # annotate("text",x=-Inf,y=Inf,hjust=-0.25,vjust=1,label=seamounts_to_plot[i])+
      coord_sf(xlim = c(extent(cobb_basemap)[1],extent(cobb_basemap)[2]), 
               ylim = c(extent(cobb_basemap)[3],extent(cobb_basemap)[4]), 
               expand = TRUE)+
      
      xlab("")+ylab("")+
      
      annotation_north_arrow(location = "br", width = unit(.5, "cm"),
                             height = unit(1., "cm"),
                             style = north_arrow_orienteering(
                               line_width = 1,
                               line_col = "black",
                               fill = c("white", "black"),
                               text_col = "black",
                               text_family = "",
                               text_face = NULL,
                               text_size = 10,
                               text_angle = 0)) +
      
      scale_fill_manual(values=c("green","yellow","red"),labels=c("low","medium","high"),na.translate=FALSE,name="VME Group")+
      ggtitle("Predicted weighted VME liklihood category")+
      
      #       fill = 'Presence', 
      #      color = 'Presence')+
      theme_dark()+theme(panel.grid = element_blank(),legend.position = c(0.8,0.2),plot.margin = unit(c(.05,.05,.25,.25),"pt"),axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 0, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1,size=5),axis.text.y=element_text(size=5))
    
    myplots[[i]]<-ggplotGrob(p)
  }
  return(myplots)
}



make_hist<-function(raster){
require(ggplot2)
  
myplots<-list()
jenks<-getBreaks(values(raster),nclass=3,method="jenks")
d4<-hist(raster,breaks=15,plot=FALSE)
d4<-data.frame(counts=d4$counts,breaks=d4$mids,cat1=cut(d4$mids,breaks=jenks))
p1<-ggplot(d4)+geom_bar(aes(x=breaks,y=counts,fill=cat1),stat="identity",alpha=0.8)+xlab("Weighted probability of occurrence")+ylab("Frequency")+
  scale_fill_manual(values=c("green","yellow","red"),name="VME probability",labels=c("Low","Medium","High"))+
  geom_vline(xintercept = jenks[2:4],linetype="dashed")

myplots[[1]]<-ggplotGrob(p1)

return(myplots)
}

    myplots[[i]]<-ggplotGrob(p)
  }
  return(myplots)
